When would the user play the game?

  -On the ay to work, on the bus/train and when waiting for short periods of time.

How to make the game sutible for that use?

  -Never has to have an online connection.
  -Short load times, user dosen't want to have to wait half of their journey to load the game.
  -Can be played in short doses.
  -Easy to navigate.
  Easy straightforward controls.
  -Player can start 'playing' as soon as possible, i.e. few menu screens between entrance to app and game.

Controls?

  -Touch screen, buttons.
  -Simple laid out buttons that easily display what the user will achieve upon pressing them.

Display?

  -Simple
  -Clear
  -Easy to read. Especially on small screened devices.